Show per-sender relationship aggregates: volume, response cadence, open threads. The unfair advantage of having local SQLite — every other email tool reasons over messages, not people

Usage: mxr sender [OPTIONS] <EMAIL>

Arguments:
  <EMAIL>  Email address (must match an existing contact)

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>  Restrict to a specific account; defaults to the only-or-default account if exactly one is configured
      --format <FORMAT>    [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help               Print help
